formattedAddress: 1 Utama Shopping Centre (Lot 146), Lebuh Bandar Utama

tip.text: Overall the food is good. The prices are reasonable too. Must try their desserts. I recommend the layer cake dipped with sesame sauce and also the glutinous rice dessert. 👍
Terrible and horrible! The presentation of food is so horrible it's gonna make you cry. The taste is normal, you can actually cook at home and it'll taste better than this. PRICE, SUPER NOT WORTH IT.
Pancake is not your ordinary pancake. It's very fluffy and soft though!
Burger portion is huge! Can actually have them for two meals. Route 66 is so so. The music is very loud though. Hope they can tone it down else the customers will be going deaf.
The shop is very small but no less, the cake quality is superb and is to die for!

tip.text: The yao char guai serves as a tasty appetizer. ☺️ Be careful not to consume sour coconut, ask for a change if they give you spoiled ones. Thai tomyam is very nice. But the crab is not fresh
Best tiramisu I've ever tasted in penang!
Churros and cronut is very special. Recommended dips are salted caramel and Nutella. Love the white chocolate cheesecake too.
Mixed berry panna cotta is lovely. Not sweet just nice.
Very nice deal they have here.
